Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
One Commerce Square is the most visible structure on the Downtown Memphis skyline. The Property offers sweeping views of the Mississippi River and
all of downtown Memphis. Tenants of One Commerce Square can easily access the City’s premier entertainment and sporting venues including
AutoZone Park (AAA Baseball), the Orpheum Theatre, FedEx Forum, and the Beale Street Entertainment District.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Since 2010, One Commerce Square has invested over $5.0 million in capital improvements including modernization of the elevators, new roofs on the office tower and annex, chiller replacements, LED lighting in the garage and numerous upgrades to the building lobby and common areas.
